00:00:12.985 --> 00:00:19.033
Hi! Welcome to your favorite show Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:28.907 --> 00:00:31.139
What are you going to cook for us today?
Sambhar Dhokla

00:00:37.534 --> 00:00:40.387
Ingredients required for Sambhar Dhokla

00:00:40.923 --> 00:00:52.120
Wheat Flour, Tomatoes, Onions, Garam Masala, 
Red Chilli Powder, Coriander Leaves, Salt, Curry Leaves &amp; Oil 

00:01:02.669 --> 00:01:07.450
First heat some oil in a pan

00:01:11.442 --> 00:01:16.374
Add some cumin seeds, mustard seeds and black gram into the pan

00:01:20.909 --> 00:01:28.203
Add some sliced onions and
 tomato pieces into the pan

00:01:29.456 --> 00:01:34.321
Now fry them for a little while

00:01:58.405 --> 00:02:05.533
Now remove the pan and grind the 
half fried tomato and onion pieces with oil 

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:22.280
Now heat a pan and add the ground tomato mix in it 

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:28.393
Now let it boil for a while

00:02:33.773 --> 00:02:44.854
Now take some wheat flour, add some
 ghee in it and make a dough out of it

00:02:45.890 --> 00:02:53.728
Now flatten the dough into a thick round layer

00:02:55.488 --> 00:03:02.049
Cut the flatten dough into small circular pieces 

00:03:06.698 --> 00:03:13.891
Now add the circular dough pieces into the boiling tomato mix

00:03:14.237 --> 00:03:19.918
Now let it cook for 10 minutes

00:03:31.335 --> 00:03:36.838
Add some garam masala into the pan &amp; mix well

00:03:45.211 --> 00:03:51.826
Add some red chilli powder into the pan &amp; mix well 

00:03:53.842 --> 00:03:58.929
Add some salt into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:08.011 --> 00:04:15.965
Add some coriander leaves &amp; 
curry leaves into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:34.894 --> 00:04:52.621
Add some boiled bengal gram into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:56.173 --> 00:05:04.056
Add some water into the pan &amp; let it cook for a while

00:05:47.984 --> 00:05:51.479
Now take the Sambhar Dhokla into a serving bowl

